# Index

## Directories
- `contracts/` — work contracts by lifecycle status (draft, active, completed)
- `docs/` — deep references and long-form analysis
- `glossary/` — domain terms and definitions
- `goals/` — goal checklists and per-goal details
- `guide/` — software development process guidance
- `notes/` — short summaries and quick references
- `prompts/` — prompt templates (file-based)
- `rules/` — persistent agent constraints and conventions
- `security-cases/` — security bug post-mortems (RCA, severity, mitigation)
- `skills/` — project-specific skill definitions
- `strategy/` — long-term objectives and invariants
- `tactics/` — situational playbooks ("if X, do Y")
- `taxonomy/` — naming and classification rules

## Files
- `meta.mdc` — portable meta-engineering rules and binding structure contract
